{"type": "article", "id": 12501, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2015-07-23T08:00:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 7415, "name": "蓝牙耳机"}, {"id": 448, "name": "家具"}, {"id": 266, "name": "椅子"}, {"id": 3786, "name": "包袋"}, {"id": 2976, "name": "灯饰"}, {"id": 9968, "name": "手机壳"}, {"id": 13346, "name": "DV"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 55, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000428efcyGD2TirBzP8lj.png", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\tLight-Light 5 by Gaspard Graulich \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这是一款极简主义的立灯，它的名字 “Light-Light 5” 来自构成灯的五个部分；大理石底座，灯绳，皮革搭扣，不锈钢支架和黄铜接口。组装起来非常简单可行，拧上灯泡便可以使用，而灯座和架子黑白两色对比，灯绳的轻巧和大理石的重量对比，彰显着设计细节上的用心。这是<a href=\"http://www.gaspardgraulich.com/V7/fr\" target=\"_blank\">设计师的个人主页</a>，点击可以查看更多作品。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071905274xdfvh2Dm7XSgu9y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.41442543\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190527T6rdDYRsLIa1BbFG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190527PHLutRb914UE8ACJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190528PZx0wyauWKAzmgqJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190529LnOKb0y7WIxwaAjk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190529CW8kfRvimwXr1eau.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071905298kU2OtgFZRjDaKAy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190530AaL0esXk593mWEuS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tHelix by Ashley Chloe\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Helix 是一款无线蓝牙耳机，来自 Ashley Chloe 公司。耳机整体设计简洁明快，配有线控和麦克风，几乎可以兼容所有可以使用蓝牙的智能手机。同时，耳机收起来以后，可以变成一个手环，佩戴在手腕上不容易丢失。颜色上有黑色、白色和红色三款可以选择，目前产品正在 Kickstarter 上面众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1889846331/helix-wearable-cuff-with-stereo-bluetooth-headphon\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071905306bCX5tD3E8rI9Jzm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190531ULaDgsh9RAcHCqIO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140221vnhJ5Y6m8XOigMAE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190531syXGrcxSv63IZEzF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190531oxbXMYr0nZyU86Is.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190532eWS8qB5h4z2J9jkP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62647059\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190532il7TNEJ8MfGRY2Bk.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60382916\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tCinematic by Lumenati\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>来自美国的 Lumenati 工作室推出了一款智能手机壳，可以把 iPhone 6 或是 6S 嵌在里面，变成一个便携的 DV 使用，它带有一个手柄方便握住使用，你还可以选择广角镜头、鱼眼镜头、长焦镜头等多种镜头。同时，和手机壳配套的还有一个 Lumenati Cinematic App，可以用来对拍摄的视频进行简单的后期编辑。这是他们的<a href=\"http://cinematicsmartcase.com/\" target=\"_blank\">官方网站</a>，点击可以查看详细信息。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190533aUIv9ujtKXAMkcwf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190534K1qRDYsGhMcWkfjm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72982885\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190534PH1wkKRyzrpcdf38.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190534l6CYkJmGWdFftNO8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190535w2FRTIAx9BHjpXon.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190536OtxTSF86D4CdvUKr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61613692\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190536RmHtTrJIZ5lkKE39.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tRay-S Speaker by Davone \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>设计师 Charles 和 Ray Eames 夫妇被誉为 20 世纪最有影响力的设计师之一，它们在 1956 年推出的 Eames lounge chair &amp; ottoman，至今仍然是经典。最近，丹麦设计公司 Davone 以此为灵感来源，推出了 “Ray-S” 扬声器，外部箱体压制 16 层榉木制成，音色丰富，解析力强。设计师把古老的经典设计和当代科技结合在一起，喜欢那款经典躺椅的相信也会对这款扬声器感兴趣。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190536W4wGm7rAhJ83cyPX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190537O5xl0vXhGcp6AU9q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00611247\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190537r8DukCyoeq7LZ3sf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33251834\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071905380EHmIpUBL5a7JW9P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49266504\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t“14” by Lukas Avena\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Lukas Avena 的这一款椅子专门为喜欢读书读报的人设计，都市年轻人常常没有足够大的起居空间，便经常会遇到没看完的书或是报纸没地方放的问题。这款椅子把普通的扶手变成了倾斜的形状，看起来就像一个报架，虽然不能储存大量的书籍，但是把正在阅读的书籍搭在上面，既节省存储空间，又方便继续阅读。这是<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/lukasave\" target=\"_blank\">设计师的个人主页</a>，点击可以查看更多作品。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190538bVNJLps8AI7QtX5g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071905394Wk9StY360ragAJs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190539tkFpCW3zj0YZefTl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190540T78q2J9uzgBhmLrl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.47407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060719054089kuA1aozB4P3rNC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tTurtle &amp; Whale Backpack by Thom Browne\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Thom Browne 最近推出 2015 年秋冬系列，其中这两款鲸鱼和海龟背包颇有故事性和趣味性，看起来童趣盎然。在细节设计上也一点都不含糊，材料使用的是全黑的皮革，精致而充满质感，当然价格也一点都不含糊。这是<a href=\"https://www.whatdropsnow.com/brands/thom-browne\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060719054102aZINkbqxuyGmAf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190542tKfEmr3M180IUJFk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190542c0d5yQb7mf2jJHtE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190543SdA7nbPtFaJlKvMY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607190543nXsor7cLFxqeOP2T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n"}